<paragraph base="F4230959" id="IFRS03_B13" principles="no"><paranum>B13</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 3"/><data name="paranum" value="B13"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS03_P0357">The guidance in <xref base="F16164357" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_TOC.dita#IFRS10_TOC0001" id="IFRS03_X0394">IFRS 10 <ph outputclass="standard_ref"><ph outputclass="standard_title">Consolidated Financial Statements</ph></ph></xref> shall be used to identify the <xref base="F4230833" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0297">acquirer<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0005"/></ph></xref>&#x2014;the entity that obtains <xref base="F4230846" href="../ifrs10/IFRS10_APPA.dita#IFRS10_APPA/IFRS10_DI0002" scope="local">control<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0053"/></ph></xref> of the <xref base="F4230829" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0296">acquiree<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0004"/></ph></xref>.              If a <xref base="F4230842" href="IFRS03_APPA.dita#IFRS03_APPA/IFRS03_P0304">business combination<ph outputclass="def_xref"><xref keyref="GLOSSARY_DI0025"/></ph></xref> has occurred but applying the guidance in IFRS 10 does not clearly indicate which of the combining entities is the acquirer, the factors in <xref base="F5311668" href="IFRS03_B14.dita#IFRS03_B14" id="IFRS03_X0397">paragraphs B14&#x2013;B18</xref> shall be considered in making that determination.</p></body></paragraph>